import React from "react";
import { Redirect } from "react-router-dom";

import AdmindashBoard from '../pages/SuperAdmin/AdminDashboard/index'

import Users from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Users/index'
import DummyUsers from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Users/dummyUsers'
import Client from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Users/ClientList'
import Writer from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Users/WriterList'

import AdminOrder from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Order/index';
import OrderPage from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Order/Orderpage'

import Project from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Project/index'
import ProjectPage from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Project/Projectpage';
import AssignProject from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Project/AssignProject'

import Services from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Services/index'
import CreateServices from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Services/CreateService';

import SubjectArea from '../pages/SuperAdmin/SubjectArea/index';
import CreateSubjectArea from '../pages/SuperAdmin/SubjectArea/CreateSubjectArea'

import Spacings from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Spacing/index';
import CreateSpacing from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Spacing/CreateSpacing';

import Library from '../pages/SuperAdmin/library/index'
import CreateLibrary from '../pages/SuperAdmin/library/Createlibrary';

import Withdrawal from '../pages/SuperAdmin/Withdrawal'


const superadminRoutes = [
    {path: "/admin-dashboard", component: AdmindashBoard},

    { path: "/admin-order", component: AdminOrder },
    { path: "/orderpage/:id?", component: OrderPage },

    { path: "/users", component: Users },
    { path: "/dummyusers", component: DummyUsers },
    { path: "/client", component: Client },
    { path: "/writer", component: Writer },

    { path: "/projects", component: Project },
    { path: "/projectspage/:id?", component: ProjectPage },
    { path: "/assignprojects", component: AssignProject },

    { path: "/services", component: Services},
    { path: "/createservice/:id?", component: CreateServices},

    { path: "/subjectarea", component: SubjectArea},
    { path: "/createsubjectarea/:id?", component: CreateSubjectArea},

    { path: "/spacing", component: Spacings},
    { path: "/createspacing/:id?", component: CreateSpacing},

    { path: "/library", component: Library},
    { path: "/createlibrary/:id?", component: CreateLibrary},

     { path: "/withdrawal", component: Withdrawal},


    { path: "/", exact: true, component: () => <Redirect to="/admin-dashboard" /> },

  ];

  export { superadminRoutes };
